#!/usr/bin/python3
"""Self-contained mechanical edge for an owner-approved production cutover.

This file is a build template, not an executable.  The release packager
replaces the five exact sentinels below and emits six distinct executables.
Each emitted artifact accepts only its own action class, validates the signed
plan and its own SHA-256, constructs a sealed child environment, and emits one
canonical, secret-free receipt.

The runtime deliberately contains no model routing or semantic policy.  It
only observes exact PostgreSQL/host state, applies reviewed bytes, restores
the exact pre-cutover state while zero writer writes are proven, and records
mechanical receipts.
"""

from __future__ import annotations

